{"type": "article", "id": 25438, "title": "电子产品配件魔方", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 163, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170332Cx5VDeaYrO1JEjNF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个魔方汇聚了连接线、U盘、读卡器、应急充电宝、手电筒和手机支架等多个功能，号称““智能手机的瑞士军刀”。所有功能巧妙结合在只有 1 英寸（2.54厘米）的空间里，将两边的线拉出也只有 3 英寸长，非常适合随身携带。其中还内置了可达 64GB 的记忆卡，另可放 9V 的电池。非常适合栓在钥匙链上。设计团队来自香港，产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wondercube-8-mobile-essentials-in-one-cubic-inch#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170327Jyq345WsH79kvd0E.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021703304OWcv9zHey2j0xPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170330QzICf80Yy97HEdrK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170331HCf3DEmKFW7ZBogY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170331Dkd7RVgflQqbK62S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}